---
import Layout from "../../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import FAQSchema from "../../../components/FAQSchema.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Carpet Cleaning Saint-Bruno-de-Montarville | Prestige Home Service"
  description="Professional carpet and upholstery cleaning in Saint-Bruno-de-Montarville. Premium truck-mount service for large properties, wool rugs, and leather furniture."
>
  <div class="split-hero-container mobile-hero-stack">
    <div class="container full-width-split">
      <div class="split-layout">
        <div class="split-content fade-in-section">
          <span class="service-cat-badge">PRESTIGE SERVICE • SAINT-BRUNO-DE-MONTARVILLE</span>
          <h1 class="split-title fade-in-up text-gradient-empire">
            Carpet Cleaning in Saint-Bruno-de-Montarville
          </h1>

          <div class="mobile-hero-slideshow fade-in-up delay-050">
            <div class="slideshow-container">
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/nettoyage-tapis-laine-jaune.webp"
              alt="Expert cleaning of a large wool rug in a beautiful Saint-Bruno home"
              class="slide active"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="eager"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/resultat-tapis-berbere-propre.webp"
              alt="Immaculate Berber carpet after deep professional cleaning in Saint-Bruno"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/camion-usine-nettoyage-empire.webp"
              alt="Empire Cleaning truck-mount parked for a Saint-Bruno intervention"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            </div>
            <div class="image-overlay-gradient"></div>
          </div>

          <div class="problem-statement fade-in-up delay-100" style="border-left-color: var(--color-accent);">
            <h3 class="problem-title" style="color: var(--color-primary);">Properties That Deserve the Best:</h3>
            <p class="problem-text">
              Saint-Bruno-de-Montarville, surrounded by the beautiful Mont-Saint-Bruno National Park, attracts homeowners who invest in their interiors. Oriental rugs, premium wool carpeting, and upholstered designer furniture deserve expert attention.
            </p>
          </div>

          <p class="lead-text fade-in-up delay-200">
            Empire Cleaning Group's certified technicians understand the value of your investments. We treat every fiber with precision—whether it's a large Berber carpet, a precious hand-knotted wool rug, or a full-grain leather sofa.
          </p>

          <div class="cta-group fade-in-up delay-300">
            <a href="tel:5148939939" class="btn btn-gradient-green pulse-btn">
              <span class="icon">📞</span> (514) 893-9939 (Saint-Bruno Service)
            </a>
            <button onclick="window.openEstimationWidget()" class="btn btn-gradient-green">
              <span class="icon">⚡</span> Instant Free Quote
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="split-image-wrapper fade-in-section delay-200">
          <div class="slideshow-container">
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/nettoyage-tapis-laine-jaune.webp"
              alt="Expert cleaning of a large wool rug in a beautiful Saint-Bruno home"
              class="slide active"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              fetchpriority="high"
              loading="eager"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/resultat-tapis-berbere-propre.webp"
              alt="Immaculate Berber carpet after deep professional cleaning in Saint-Bruno"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
            <img
              src="/images/catalog/camion-usine-nettoyage-empire.webp"
              alt="Empire Cleaning truck-mount parked for a Saint-Bruno intervention"
              class="slide"
              width="1200"
              height="800"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="image-overlay-gradient"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-layout">
        <div class="service-main">
          <div class="fade-in-section delay-100">
            <h2 class="section-title text-gradient-empire">
              Why Saint-Bruno Trusts Our Specialists?
            </h2>
            <p>
              Saint-Bruno homeowners are discerning—and rightly so. Here is what sets us apart from common cleaning services:
            </p>
            <ul class="benefit-list" style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
              <li>
                <strong>Wool & Silk Rug Expertise:</strong> Before applying anything, we test the pH of your rug's natural dyes. An overly alkaline product on wool can cause irreversible color bleeding. Our neutral or mildly acidic agents clean deeply while preserving the original vibrancy of your antique or hand-knotted rugs.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Leather Furniture Treatment:</strong> Saint-Bruno is known for premium interiors. If you own a Natuzzi, Palliser, or other high-end leather sofa, our technicians use a professional-grade leather conditioner that cleans without drying out the leather pores.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Optional Stain Protector Application:</strong> After a deep clean, you can opt for the application of a fluorochemical protector (similar to Scotchgard) that repels future liquid spills—ideal for families with active young children.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Wide Staircase Cleaning:</strong> The grand open-concept staircases in large Saint-Bruno homes often feature beautiful carpeting. Our specialized stair tool ensures edge-to-edge extraction without overflowing onto adjacent hardwood.
              </li>
              <li>
                <strong>Fully Self-Sufficient Truck:</strong> Our trucks bring their own purified, pre-heated water and leave with all the waste water. No use of your indoor plumbing, zero impact on your home's water pressure.
              </li>
            </ul>

            <div style="margin-top: 3rem; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid var(--color-accent); padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px;">
              <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                🌲 Saint-Bruno: The Forest at Your Doorstep
              </h3>
              <p>
                The natural beauty of Saint-Bruno comes with a trade-off: the spring pollen from Mont-Saint-Bruno National Park and autumn leaves penetrate indoor spaces and embed into your carpet fibers. Annual professional truck-mount cleaning removes these seasonal allergens and significantly improves the indoor air quality of your home.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: 3rem;">
              <hr class="separator" />
              <h3>Easy Access for Our Equipment</h3>
              <p>
                The majority of properties in Saint-Bruno have long driveways that make access easy for our truck-mounts. Our 200-foot (60-meter) hoses allow us to reach every room of your residence directly from the driveway.
              </p>
              <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                Have a delicate oriental rug that deserves special care? Read our <a href="/en/conseils/erreurs-taches-tapis" style="color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: bold;">guide on the mistakes to avoid</a> before any stain intervention.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-layout" style="display: block;">
        <div class="service-main" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">

          <div class="zones-section" style="margin-top: 3rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
            <h3 style="color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.4rem;">Sectors & Nearby Cities We Serve</h3>
            <div class="city-group">
              <div class="badges-container">
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Old Saint-Bruno (Heritage Sector)</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Montarville & Boisé Sectors</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Sainte-Julie (Nearby)</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 Beloeil (Nearby)</span>
                <span class="badge badge-blue">📍 McMasterville</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="contact-footer">Schedule your Saint-Bruno cleaning: <strong>(514) 893-9939</strong>.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="fade-in-section delay-300" style="margin-top: 3rem;">
            <h2 class="section-title text-gradient-empire">
              Frequently Asked Questions — Saint-Bruno-de-Montarville
            </h2>
            <FAQSchema
              faqs={[
                {
                  question: "I have a beautiful hand-knotted Persian wool rug. Can you clean it without damaging the natural dyes?",
                  answer: "Absolutely. This is one of our specialties. We first test the pH of the dyes in a discrete area. We then use an enzymatic solution with a slightly acidic pH that cleans effectively with zero risk of color bleeding, thus preserving the vivacity and integrity of your Persian rug's colors.",
                },
                {
                  question: "My Palliser leather sectional has a grease stain. Can it be treated?",
                  answer: "Yes. Grease stains on leather are treatable with our specialized leather cleaner containing gentle emulsifying agents. After cleaning, we apply a professional leather conditioner to restore its suppleness and natural hydration.",
                },
                {
                  question: "Could cleaning my carpets trigger my seasonal allergies?",
                  answer: "On the contrary, our cleaning is a solution against allergies. Our hot steam extraction removes dust mites, Mont-Saint-Bruno park pollen, and pet dander embedded in your fibers. After our visit, the indoor air quality in your home should improve noticeably.",
                },
                {
                  question: "Do you clean basement carpeting in Saint-Bruno where there may be humidity issues?",
                  answer: "Yes, we regularly treat basements. If your basement has moisture concerns, we also recommend our preventive anti-mold treatment in addition to the standard cleaning, to prevent the carpet from becoming a breeding ground for spores.",
                }
              ]}
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<script>
  document.querySelectorAll(".slideshow-container").forEach((container) => {
    const slides = container.querySelectorAll(".slide");
    if (slides.length <= 1) return;
    let currentSlide = 0;
    setInterval(() => {
      slides[currentSlide].classList.remove("active");
      currentSlide = (currentSlide + 1) % slides.length;
      slides[currentSlide].classList.add("active");
    }, 4000);
  });
</script>

<style>
  .split-hero-container { background-color: #fff; padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; overflow: hidden; width: 100vw; }
  .full-width-split { width: 100%; max-width: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .split-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 0; align-items: stretch; min-height: 80vh; }
  .split-content { background-color: #ffffff; padding: 100px 4rem 4rem 10%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center; position: relative; z-index: 2; }
  .service-cat-badge { text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--color-accent); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 2px; font-size: 0.85rem; display: block; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .split-title { font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 3.5vw, 4rem); color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 2rem; line-height: 1.1; }
  .city-group { margin-bottom: 1.5rem; }
  .badges-container { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .badge { padding: 0.4rem 0.9rem; border-radius: 20px; font-size: 0.9rem; border: 1px solid transparent; }
  .badge-blue { background: #e8f4fd; border-color: #c5dff0; }
  .problem-statement { background: #ffffff; border-left: 4px solid #ff4444; padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 0; margin-bottom: 2rem; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(174, 206, 235, 0.3); }
  .problem-title { font-size: 1rem; color: #cc0000; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 700; }
  .problem-text { font-size: 1.05rem; color: var(--color-text-main); font-style: italic; }
  .lead-text { font-size: 1.15rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--color-text-main); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; max-width: 650px; }
  .cta-group { display: flex; gap: 1rem; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  @media (max-width: 900px) { .cta-group { display: none !important; } }
  .split-image-wrapper { position: relative; height: 100%; min-height: 500px; width: 100%; }
  .slideshow-container { position: relative; width: 100%; height: 100%; overflow: hidden; }
  .slideshow-container img.slide {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100% !important;
    height: 100% !important;
    object-fit: cover !important;
    object-position: center !important;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 1.5s ease-in-out;
  }
  .slideshow-container img.slide.active { opacity: 1; }
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .split-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; min-height: auto; }
    .lead-text { max-width: 100%; }
  }
  .service-layout { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 5rem; }
  .section-title { font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--color-primary); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; display: inline-block; }
  .separator { border: 0; height: 1px; background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1); margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  .benefit-list { margin: 2rem 0; list-style: none; padding: 0; }
  .benefit-list li { margin-bottom: 1rem; padding-left: 1.5rem; position: relative; font-size: 1.05rem; }
  .benefit-list li::before { content: "✓"; color: #d32f2f; position: absolute; left: 0; font-weight: bold; }
  .contact-footer { margin-top: 1.5rem; font-style: italic; color: #666; }
</style>
